{"tid":1847230,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公僕明起留家工作至2月2日　緊急和公共服務人員除外","createTime":"2020-01-28T03:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T04:52:31.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6886e1c90b6141480fc1b70cfc073bb95c6c6884","tid":1847230,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"為了盡量減低疫情在社區擴散的風險，政府發言人今日宣布，政府部門將會於農曆新年假期後（即明日，1月29日起）實施特別上班安排。除了提供緊急和必須公共服務的人員外，政府僱員在假期後無需返回寫字樓辦公，而是留在家中工作。<br />\n<br />\n有關安排暫定實行至2月2日，政府屆時會再檢視情況。政府發言人呼籲私人機構在可行情況下，作類似安排。個別政府部門會就受影響的公共服務作出公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1189420/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%85%AC%E5%83%95%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E7%95%99%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%B32%E6%9C%882%E6%97%A5-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1189420%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2583%2595%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2587%25B32%25E6%259C%25882%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%25A4%2596&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=4221ebb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1189420%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2583%2595%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2587%25B32%25E6%259C%25882%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%